#hash((content-digest . "e4027ffa8adc9c41f0e58e300bcd9585b2a45c6da2c8a556aaa601faf0a83d5d") (content-digest-command . "git diff --binary origin/main...HEAD -- . (excluding gsd-wave-evidence/reviews/validation) | sha256sum") (non-blocking-findings . ()) (report . "APPROVED. W4 closes three bounded session/frontend truth defects. A-08/F-06: TUI handle-compaction-lifecycle now requires event-for-current-session? in addition to request-id correlation; foreign-session compact events no longer clear pending status or append terminal transcript entries (4/4 red-first TUI reducer tests). A-09/F-11: GUI run-gui-with-runtime delegates session construction to the canonical open-or-resume resolver via a new gui-resolve-session seam; a requested id resumes the exact session (no sibling) and a missing id fails before window launch (3/3 red-first GUI resume tests). A-10/F-14: read-session-metadata reports the LATEST model-change chronologically (not the first); sessions-info counts tool-call content parts inside production assistant messages plus legacy top-level compatibility (2/2 new red-first metadata tests). Focused 120; tui 84 files 1316; fast 1047 files 15394; smoke 289; arch 183; workflows 146; lint 23 PASS 0 failures. No real-provider runs (prohibited until W6).") (reviewed-sha . "49da3c5867b92d236e34bcfe13613f07d10bd4f2") (reviewer . "orchestrator pre-merge evidence") (scope . "v0.99.52 W4 #8768 compact session correlation, GUI resume, metadata truth") (timestamp . "2026-07-19T20:30:00Z") (verdict . "APPROVED"))
